---
import DocsLayout from '../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Examples" description="Theme showcase and copy-paste form and layout examples using Rizzo CSS components and design tokens.">
  <section>
    <p>These example pages show how to combine Rizzo CSS components and tokens into common patterns. Copy snippets into your project or use them as a starting point.</p>

    <h2 id="theme-showcase">Theme showcase</h2>
    <p>See all 14 themes in one place with a live preview. Switch themes and copy the <code>data-theme</code> snippet for your app.</p>
    <p><a href="/themes" class="btn btn-primary">Open theme showcase</a></p>

    <h2 id="form-layout-examples">Form &amp; layout examples</h2>
    <p>Copy-paste examples for login and contact forms, dashboard stats cards, card grids, and settings panels. All use Rizzo form components, cards, and semantic tokens.</p>
    <p><a href="/docs/examples/form-layouts" class="btn btn-outline">Form &amp; layout examples</a></p>

    <h2 id="blocks">Pre-built blocks</h2>
    <p>Full-page layouts (dashboard, docs shell) that you can scaffold with the CLI or copy from the Blocks section.</p>
    <p><a href="/blocks" class="btn btn-outline">Browse blocks</a></p>
  </section>
</DocsLayout>
